data.description: Welcome to your new home! Here is a captivating 3-bedroom, 3-bathroom home that seamlessly blends modern elegance with timeless charm. Step into the remodeled chef's kitchen, featuring ample cabinet space and a beautifully spacious island—ideal for both culinary enthusiasts and those who love to entertain. The remodeled bathrooms showcase elegant finishes, creating a spa-like retreat within the comfort of your own home. Updates in this home has been carefully curated to enhance both style and functionality. Descend into the finished basement, offering extra space for entertaining and everyday living. A versatile flex room awaits, perfect for use as an office or recreation room. Adjacent to this is an inviting outdoor sunroom—a perfect spot to unwind, relax, or entertain family and friends. Step out back to discover your private oasis—a refreshing in-ground pool that invites relaxation and recreation, whether you're hosting gatherings or simply enjoying a quiet day in the sun. For those with a passion for projects, the large garage/workshop provides ample space for creative endeavors. This multipurpose area can accommodate your vehicle or any hobby and DIY project you have in mind. Make this house your home and experience the perfect blend of luxury, comfort, and endless possibilities. Schedule your showing today!
